Class JdbcFlightOperationsService

java.lang.Object
com.gcu.agms.service.impl.JdbcFlightOperationsService
All Implemented Interfaces:
FlightOperationsService
@Service("jdbcFlightOperationsService") @Primary public class JdbcFlightOperationsService extends Object implements FlightOperationsService
JDBC implementation of the FlightOperationsService interface. This service uses database repositories to access and manage flight and maintenance data.
